5. Runtime dependencies
================================================================================

The translator depends on FreeCAD as a runtime (loaded via Python module
import; not bundled). Anyone running the translator needs FreeCAD installed
separately, typically via conda-forge. FreeCAD itself is LGPL-2.0-or-later;
depending on it as a runtime does not impose obligations on this project's
own source code, but it does require that any redistributed *binary* that
links against FreeCAD preserves the LGPL.

